ATTRIBUTION NOTICE:

This software is based on the original SNID (SuperNova IDentification) algorithm
developed by St√©phane Blondin and John L. Tonry.

Original SNID Reference:
"Determining the Type, Redshift, and Age of a Supernova Spectrum"
Blondin, S. & Tonry, J. L. 2007, ApJ, 666, 1024

SNID SAGE represents a complete Python rewrite and enhancement of the original
Fortran SNID code, developed by Fiorenzo Stoppa. 